title: 27: Moments Chasing Stability
itunes:title: Moments Chasing Stability
description: We’re always working towards what we don’t have, and I think it’s time for us all to focus on the more important things. Like the simple ones, love, laughter and finding contentment in the current moment.
itunes:author: Lexi Hidalgo
